    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Discretization error and numerical solver error exceed required levels. The remaining six factors are scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 at MRL 2. The model form factor was evaluated through qualitative assessment with supporting sensitivity analysis and expert review, confirming adequacy for the CPB hemolysis COU. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the intended use decision.",
